original_title: Game Player's Gametape for Nintendo Cartridges - Vol. 1, No. 4
overview: A video strategy guide tutorial released by Game Player's magazine that covers Bases Loaded, Bandai Golf, Baseball Stars, Super Dodge Ball, Goal, Hoops, Tecmo Bowl and Lee Trevino's Fighting Golf.
